 />\n<br />\nPPC 依科對我依啲唔識英文既人黎講最麻煩，簡稱世史，要我寫成千字既英文assignment的確幾吃力<br />\n<br />\n中文<br />\n<br />\n總之sem1就4科英文教既加1科中文<br />\n<br />\nSem2 就開始俾你揀啲選修科，你最多可以揀到2科中文，一科古文加科現代文<br />\n<br />\n其餘就係<br />\n<br />\nEAP2<br />\n<br />\n以下二選一<br />\n<br />\nModern World/Critical thinking<br />\n<br />\nPhilosophy/ICT<br />\n<br />\n所以對我依啲英文文盲黎講，係幾吃力既，不過如果你英文幾好既話，或者反而會係件好事黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/015617_84dac9c08d9ed54283e7ed937bdd0b9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F015617_84dac9c08d9ed54283e7ed937bdd0b9b.jpg&h=53412673&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28da42ac2c70ae15113e1d818b49f5a96e25987a","tid":740233,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T18:00:39.000Z","msg":"thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我高中三年完全無掂過英文，裸考得隻3<br />\n係咪會唔夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12dcecaaa440015444f7ea2be72d50024d71d724","tid":740233,"uid":67219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7180e414f7179e587aa591befcfcb12eb1f01e2","tid":740233,"uid":182231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"829265211dffc8f4e28bb02f5e7bfbc53a6d292e","tid":740233,"uid":67219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T16:55:44.000Z","msg":"Cie中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T17:14:08.000Z","msg":"依個又真係無咩點考慮過，點解咁講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T18:03:03.000Z","msg":"今年有幾個入返中大中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42167778ed7c88699fa50a041cad95b502cd9da2","tid":740233,"uid":74896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"456f0d3c0dc7d0fd259b9237e955fe7beccbbd06","tid":740233,"uid":182231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T16:43:51.000Z","msg":"人生第一個po　有無人可以幫下我<br />\n<br />\n我英文2<br />\n<br />\n本身上年報左hkuspace既中文糸讀<br />\n<br />\n但係英文真係太弱，所以最後gpa都係過唔到3<br />\n<br />\n近排搵左好多資料，但係都係諗唔到報邊間好<br />\n<br />\nhkcc　係asso既評價上就最好，但好似同space一樣都避唔開英文，好驚會炒多次<br />\n<br />\ncccu　感覺上就好似小啲英文讀，但評價上好似有啲褒貶不一<br />\n<br />\ncuscs　既hd中文系基本上就掂得最小英文，但評價比較差，又驚升唔到上ugc<br />\n<br />\nling u　感覺課程上都唔錯，但升翻上大學既機會點都比唔上 hkcc 同cccu<br />\n<br />\n所以　如果就升學機率方面<br />\n<br />\nhkcc  &gt;  space  &gt;  cccu  &gt;  ling u  &gt;  cuscs<br />\n<br />\n如果就課程既中文百分比方面<br />\n<br />\ncuscs  &gt;  ling u  &gt;  cccu  &gt;  hkcc  &gt;space<br />\n<br />\n我想問下我個排序有無錯<br />\n<br />\n如果要權衡翻升學同能力既話，我應該點揀好<br />\n<br />\n我係space上堂，可以有成一大半都聽唔明個lecturer講咩<br />\n<br />\n我應該點揀先可以唔好死得咁甘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T18:05:29.000Z","msg":"唔識英文cccu"},{"pid":"edd93c642acccea44adefbfafd10393ecc1f091c","tid":740233,"uid":74896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T18:06:41.000Z","msg":"認真，cccu acs對英文要求低到極點，基本上唔太影響gpa"},{"pid":"4aeb149c3252e298c2fcefe46d73980c0007ea9f","tid":740233,"uid":182231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28da42ac2c70ae15113e1d818b49f5a96e25987a","tid":740233,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T18:00:39.000Z","msg":"thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我高中三年完全無掂過英文，裸考得隻3<br />\n係咪會唔夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T18:07:06.000Z","msg":"我中學中中，但係我英文尾20。係咁死背英文，係咁補習，但係得2。<br />\n<br />\n依個就係我地既分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過英文勁又真係好大優勢既<br />\n<br />\n不過聽得明lecturer講咩應該都夠　掛"},{"pid":"180cb81096cdb051c3ae82359b7277c4d41f7313","tid":740233,"uid":74896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4aeb149c3252e298c2fcefe46d73980c0007ea9f","tid":740233,"uid":182231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28da42ac2c70ae15113e1d818b49f5a96e25987a","tid":740233,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T18:00:39.